{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Ragtag Heroes is a co-op roguelike deckbuilder for up to 3 players! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Craft your own deck, defeat powerful foes in strategic combat, collect rare cards and relics and save the realm together!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067070/extras/Steam_Header_Graphics_20_.png?t=1737536856\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067070/extras/NewSpacing.gif?t=1737536856\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Push attacking monsters away from weakened heroes and bring your melee attackers in close range to deliver deadly blows. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Lock monsters in place or punish them for moving around - but watch out as they might do the same to you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067070/extras/Steam_Header_Graphics_21_.png?t=1737536856\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067070/extras/synergylite.gif?t=1737536856\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each hero has their own strengths and weaknesses and allows for a variety of strategies in building their deck. They also synergize differently with other heroes from the roster - so by switching team mates you can explore different team tactics each run.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067070/extras/Steam_Header_Graphics_18_.png?t=1737536856\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067070/extras/Initiative2.gif?t=1737536856\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Initiative determines the order of turns in combat. Strategically lowering your opponents' initiative allows your heroes to act sooner. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You may even concentrate your efforts on reducing one enemy's initiative to zero to stun them, forcing them to skip a turn.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067070/extras/Steam_Header_Graphics_4_.png?t=1737536856\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067070/extras/BraveDefault.gif?t=1737536856\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Brave and Default add an extra layer to your strategy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u201cBrave\u201d will grant you more energy for your current turn, but you will become stunned and will have to pass the next one. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Or &quot;Default&quot; your turn without performing any actions and you'll increase your hero\u2019s energy by 1 for the remaining battle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067070/extras/Steam_Header_Graphics_19_.png?t=1737536856\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> 4+ heroes with their own set of cards</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> 300+ different cards</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> 100+ items to be found</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> 50+ unique combat encounters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> 40+ mysterious story encounters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> co-op multiplayer both locally and online with up to 3 players </p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_a